{"tid":164338,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"渣打延長有薪產假　十二週增至二十週","createTime":"2017-03-20T14:52:24.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-20T16:46:04.000Z","uid":29093,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"19f6bea6b34975f3909df8990c2414a79ecba9cb","tid":164338,"uid":29093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T14:52:24.000Z","msg":"渣打延長有薪產假　十二週增至二十週<br />\n2017/3/20 &mdash; 13:55<br />\n<br />\n渣打銀行宣佈，為創造家庭友善的工作環境，將有薪產假由現行的12星期，延長至20星期，侍產假及領養兒童的有薪假，則由 5 日 增至兩星期。<br />\n<br />\n除此以外，渣打亦推出靈活工作安排政策，視乎員工職務及上司批核，員工可選擇「在家工作」、「彈性工作時間」及「兼職工作」，以滿足僱員個人目標及專業發展需要。<br />\n<br />\n同時，渣打銀行於本月 1 起，由加入該行逾 25 年的禤惠儀接任退休的陳秀梅，出任行政總裁。據《蘋果日報》報道，渣打銀行香港行政級別高管團隊中，女性約佔一伴。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/society/%E6%B8%A3%E6%89%93%E5%BB%B6%E9%95%B7%E6%9C%89%E8%96%AA%E7%94%A2%E5%81%87-%E5%8D%81%E4%BA%8C%E9%80%B1%E5%A2%9E%E8%87%B3%E4%BA%8C%E5%8D%81%E9%80%B1/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E6%25B8%25A3%25E6%2589%2593%25E5%25BB%25B6%25E9%2595%25B7%25E6%259C%2589%25E8%2596%25AA%25E7%2594%25A2%25E5%2581%2587-%25E5%258D%2581%25E4%25BA%258C%25E9%2580%25B1%25E5%25A2%259E%25E8%2587%25B3%25E4%25BA%258C%25E5%258D%2581%25E9%2580%25B1%2F&d=N3SWmacea4shigR4hA2Em7DFWuQMdHqkD4FeOi%2BWxPk%3D&h=93b051aa\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E6%25B8%25A3%25E6%2589%2593%25E5%25BB%25B6%25E9%2595%25B7%25E6%259C%2589%25E8%2596%25AA%25E7%2594%25A2%25E5%2581%2587-%25E5%258D%2581%25E4%25BA%258C%25E9%2580%25B1%25E5%25A2%259E%25E8%2587%25B3%25E4%25BA%258C%25E5%258D%2581%25E9%2580%25B1%2F&h=13d6baf1\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/society/%E6%B8%A3%E6%89%93%E5%BB%B6%E9%95%B7%E6%9C%89%E8%96%AA%E7%94%A2%E5%81%87-%E5%8D%81%E4%BA%8C%E9%80%B1%E5%A2%9E%E8%87%B3%E4%BA%8C%E5%8D%81%E9%80%B1/</a>"},{"pid":"9f7ec4fd782d0d3ccbe511bfc72260664984f008","tid":164338,"uid":5725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T14:53:32.000Z","msg":"女權